original_title: Commander Kellie & the Superkids: Armor of Light
overview: NME serves unrelenting as Major Dread is determined to destroy the broadcasts of SKTV. He enlists Darkmaster to serve as a hero to the world in order to sway viewers from SKTV. A rally is planned in order to draw even more attention to the dark side. But Commander Kellie enlists her own force of God's Word. And with the help of Pastor Daniel Lyon, the true light of God's Word is shed upon NME's darkness.
title: Commander Kellie & the Superkids: Armor of Light
